{"tid":887910,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余安安喪屍般催撐場 曾志偉：晚晚撞鬼咁","createTime":"2018-11-03T09:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T10:20:27.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0726d138dfcd521dacb165912c6b1227aa1c71","tid":887910,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%99%E5%AE%89%E5%AE%89%E5%96%AA%E5%B1%8D%E8%88%AC%E5%82%AC%E6%92%90%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89-%E6%99%9A%E6%99%9A%E6%92%9E%E9%AC%BC%E5%92%81-135400815.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BD%2599%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2596%25AA%25E5%25B1%258D%25E8%2588%25AC%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589-%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%2592%259E%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E5%2592%2581-135400815.html&d=PW3Ylk1m1Fd%2FEhJoOayKxBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4754f011\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%99%E5%AE%89%E5%AE%89%E5%96%AA%E5%B1%8D%E8%88%AC%E5%82%AC%E6%92%90%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89-%E6%99%9A%E6%99%9A%E6%92%9E%E9%AC%BC%E5%92%81-135400815.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wYHlew2urnB9c2ULF1R3vg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9NDA3O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181027a220629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwYHlew2urnB9c2ULF1R3vg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9NDA3O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181027a220629.jpg&h=9a1ebc92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余安安為慈善碌人情卡催志偉返港出席活動。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】曾志偉、余安安、薛凱琪（Fiona）等昨晚出席萬聖節慈善活動，為奧比斯籌款。活動發起人之一余安安化身「護眼勇士」參與街頭巡遊，她笑言首次在街頭跳舞巡遊非常好玩。至於志偉則特別從四川返港參與活動，笑指余安安之前每日都像喪屍一樣提醒志偉要出席，令他晚晚像撞鬼一樣。余安安則笑謂每日都提兩次，說：「本來個活動舊年搞，但因為打風延至今年，今次籌款無目標，當然愈多愈好。」志偉則不改風趣作風，不停大搞爛gag，說：「嚟緊都打風，知唔知個風叫咩名？Helloween（wind）呀。」<br />\n<br />\n志偉透露此行到四川是為香港演藝人內地發展協進會（內協會）分點視察，繼香港、北京、橫店之後，未來將在四川成立據點。Fiona透露早前受眼疾困擾，估計因拍劇長期戴隱形眼鏡，又沒有足夠休息，故不停流眼水，所以個幾月前做了激光矯視。Fiona笑言明白眼睛健康的重要性，但手術第二日已飛往內地工作。（攝影：朱偉彥）"},{"pid":"be270c8b68566703efdfce0144f7756e318b8f48","tid":887910,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be48b552c01e53f0971cd32f8b58465c01ef167c","tid":887910,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T10:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec4d5471df0c569f65346385441a34e0e0ebae6","tid":887910,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"同淥死誰手有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb76a14ddc36591464efd9076524b66f7d195cd1","tid":887910,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}